<br>
Use the search engine to look for armor for your race/class...you can even set a maximum price.  I found this very helpful for finding out what is out there.  You can even sort according to AC.  Look for a while before you buy.<br>
<br>
My best guess for starting out with 900pp is to purchase crafted, unless something with better AC shows up on your search for that slot.  Most crafted pieces seem to be under 200pp now.  You can also get cheap 1h weapons for 100-200pp, some even with a proc.<br>
